title: Moving to a Major City, Dating, Setting Boundaries, and Therapy ft Danielle and Brooke
description:
Are you a Danielle or are you a Brooke? They both join us this episode to talk about how they balance their content creating careers with dating, socializing, and more while taking on New York!
